# Everything directly in .objectiveai/bin/ is a downloaded artifact — the
# objectiveai release binaries (objectiveai, objectiveai-api, …) and the
# version.txt install marker written by test-prepare-objectiveai.sh —
# EXCEPT this file and the committed plugins/ tree.
#
# `/*` is anchored + non-recursive: it only ignores bin/'s direct
# children, so it leaves the plugins/ subtree alone (governed by the
# nested plugins/.../{cli,viewer}/.gitignore files). version.txt is a
# direct child, so it's ignored here too.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/plugins/
